i2c Directory Reference

Directories

Files

file  I2C.h
 This is the header file for the I2C master driver which exposes the data structures and exported API which can be used by the applications to use the I2C master driver.
 
file  I2CSlave.h
 This is the header file for the I2C slave driver which exposes the data structures and exported API which can be used by the applications to use the I2C slave driver.
